headline: West Pharmaceutical Services (WST): Exploring Valuation as Analyst Confidence Grows Ahead of Q3 Earnings
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services (WST) is drawing fresh interest from investors as it prepares to announce its third-quarter earnings. Analysts have flagged the company’s improving outlook, with easing inventory challenges and a focus on long-term growth strategies. See our latest analysis for West Pharmaceutical Services. After a challenging start to the year, West Pharmaceutical Services has seen renewed momentum, with a 16% gain in the last 90 days helping to offset some of the weakness...
